tel 1.0

# A multi-document stream (§6.1): three independent TEL documents separated by
# document-separator lines (a line of exactly two sigil characters, `##`). Each
# document has its own pragma and is parsed independently. Streaming parsing
# yields all three; single-document parsing reads only the first and stops at
# the first `##`.

event   deploy
service api
status  started
##
tel 1.0

event   deploy
service api
status  succeeded
##
tel 1.0

event   deploy
service web
status  started
